name: Kattegatcenteret

name: ULTA Beauty

comment: Open 24/7, no entry fee.

name: Cagnes-sur-Mer central station
directions: Next to the ticket office at the main entrance

name: Target
directions: left side of the store next to the pharmacy

name: OMS (oral maxillofacial surgery group)

comment: (Supposed to be or patients only?) Just walk into stall, the desk isn't by them so they won't stop you. Then leave immdeatly after using.

name: Bagel Street Cafe
street: The Livery Shopping Center West, 316 Sycamore Valley Rd

name: Weber's

name: Edward B. Bunn, S.J. Intercultural Center (ICC)

name: Starbucks

name: Salisbury University Guerrieri Academic Commins

name: The Beet

name: Market North
comment: Single-person, gender neutral restrooms.

name: Whitman Hall
directions: If you go in the front door (from a longer walkway outside) go toward the vending machines and then turn to the left. The bathroom is to the left once you turn. If you go in the back door (by the smaller parking lot, has stairs) go in the doors and either left or right (it's just a square) and go to the other side. There will be doors that lead to the main hallway of the building. Walk out of those and the bathroom is on the right, where the wall is jutting out.
comment: Accessible single stall with changing table. Gendered bathrooms are also available in the same area.

name: Eisenhower Hall
comment: One of my favorite unisex bathrooms

name: Target
directions: A single toilet, family restroom near the customer service desk.

name: University of New Mexico - Gallup Branch
directions: There one unisex restroom in Gurley Hall near IT and a couple in the lower level of the Zollinger Library.

name: Applebees
comment: It's transgender friendly

name: Starbucks
directions: Near the enterance. Gender neutral single occupant

name: Coffee by Design

name: Tatte Bakery

name: Racing Magpie

name: Starbucks

name: Togo's
comment: Must be a "paying customer"

name: Lipstick Lounge

comment: This is a gay bar in East Nashville. Though there is a private, unisex bathroom on the second floor, the gendered bathrooms on the first floor are fairly trans-friendly.

name: Finnkino Sello
directions:
Elokuvateatterissa kauppakeskus Sellon rakennuksen länsiosassa. Teatterin pääovista sisään katutasolle. Lipunmyynnin ja ravintola Retron välissä on suojaisa ja rauhallinen käytävä, jonka varrella inva-wc. Maksuton, vapaa pääsy. 
Movie theater in the west part of the shopping center Sello. Go through the main entrance of the movie theater. There is a gender neutral accessible toilet in the quiet corridor between the movie ticket sale and the Retro restaurant. Free of charge.

name: Citgo
directions: It is in the back right corner

name: Claude T. Bissell Building
directions: On the third and fifth floor of the bissell building. Building is located on the North side of Robarts Library. Faculty of Information is written on the side and an accessibility ramp is located on the west side of the building. To get to bathrooms take the elevator to preferred floor, and turn right into the washroom alcove.

name: Student Recreation Center, West Virginia University
directions: Two restrooms in the admin suite on the ground level. Two lockerrooms down near the entrance to the pool.

name: Diablo Subaru

comment: Bathrooms are accessible from upstairs sales area

name: Jack Sprat
directions: In the back right of restaurant

name: Matchbox
directions: Beyond the bar on the right. Lowest level.
comment: Medium price restaurant. No key to use the restroom, just knock. There are two single stall locking rooms; each says M/W on the door.
